        <updateDate>2021-09-20T18:57:08Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Online Privacy Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill establishes certain online privacy rights for personal information (including contents of communications) and certain requirements for data processors, service providers, and third parties. The bill also establishes the U.S. Digital Privacy Agency.<br /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
